                     Significant changes in SPORCO
                     -----------------------------

Version (M) 0.0.4 (2016-04-21)

  * Various small changes and bug fixes
  * Added GPU code re-contributed under new license


Version (M) 0.0.3 (2015-12-16)

  * Various small changes and bug fixes
  * Changed license from GPL to BSD
  * Removed GPU code contributed under previous license


Version (M) 0.0.2 (2015-08-07)

  * Fixed dead links in Data/getdata.sh script
  * Modified file path construction for improved Windows compatibility
  * Added GPU versions of convolutional codes contributed by Ping-Keng Jao
  * Fixed bug in auto rho mechanism in elnet function
  * Added NonNegCoef option to some functions
  * Renamed (c)bpdndliu to (c)bpdndl
  * Fixed bugs in handling of NoBndryCross and DictFilterSizes options in
    cbpdndl


Version (M) 0.0.1 (2015-05-09)

  * Initial release
